            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間16日09:53，恆生科技指數下跌149.45點（或3%），暫報4832.15點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+9.05%</li><li>近 1 月：-15.29%</li><li>近 3 月：+14.16%</li><li>近 6 月：+11.92%</li><li>今年以來：+11.49%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>林業及木材概念領跌-2.83%。其中    大森控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01580:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01580\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01580-HK</a>)            下跌        6.67%            ;        信保環球控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00723:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00723\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00723-HK</a>)            下跌        6%            ;        曼妠(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08186:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08186\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08186-HK</a>)            下跌        4.76%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大中華區概念領跌-2.60%。其中    ＸＬ二南方恒科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07226:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07226\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07226-HK</a>)            下跌        4.44%            ;        ＦＬ二富邦台灣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07232:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https:/